The paper deals with optimization problems related to wireless sensor networks, specifically energy-harvesting wireless sensor networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of computer simulations to assess performance, which could indicate a focus on Multimedia (cs.MM) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT, cs.NI, and cs.SY, followed by cs.MM and cs.LG.
